data.description: Embrace the perfect blend of rural serenity & contemporary living with this spacious 5 bedroom 3.5 bath ranch in Mount Horeb. Featuring an inviting, open concept layout seamlessly connecting living, dining, & kitchen areas, this property offers the perfect space for family gatherings & entertaining. Newly finished LL, completed in 2023 extends the living space even further. This light-filled space offers 2 addt'l bdrms, fitness area, work space, full bath & offers endless possibilities for customization to suit your unique needs. The outdoor space is equally impressive with the property backing onto scenic farmland & a mere one-minute stroll from the serene Military Ridge Trail. Don't miss the opportunity to make this extraordinary home yours. This property truly has it all.
